{"tid":1891073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李克強在北京視察口罩工廠　力爭實現每日生產過億口罩！","createTime":"2020-02-21T14:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T10:07:01.000Z","uid":63113,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5631948cf517a6da84cc93737e8abc0ed5b42e22","tid":1891073,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:24:53.000Z","msg":"國務院總理李克強今日到北京海淀區一家工廠，視察口罩生產。這家工廠原本是高端醫療器械製造商，通過與央企合作，迅速引入生產線改為生產口罩。<br />\n<br />\n現時內地每日可以生產4300多萬個口罩，李克強表示，要求在短時間內進一步擴大產能，力爭早日實現每日生產過億個口罩，廠商表示目前仍然缺少關鍵設備，李克強要求有關部門幫助加快解決。<br />\n<br />\n李克強強調，口罩現時對醫護人員來說，就是「武器」，對老百姓來說就是「盾牌」，口罩不單是防疫的有力保障，也是有序復工復產的基本條件，是民眾的心理安全屏障，現時需要與時間競賽，各生產企業一定要開足馬力擴大產能，保質保量保障供應。李克強又叫企業放心，一旦出現供過於求，國家將對多餘的設備和口罩「兜底收儲」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510022-20200221.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510022-20200221.htm&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAGXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=96af87e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510022-20200221.htm&h=b456264e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510022-20200221.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8aea3958e9fd3b41d841e18c52ffb926a80f260d","tid":1891073,"uid":86509,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:25:44.000Z","msg":"人有多大膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc051af9a751a1850394cfa23dc4a5113285bd01","tid":1891073,"uid":152123,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDVDOJd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDVDOJd.gif&h=77e01c87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ed68511c747062a2464fb3e704ddb92d8761875","tid":1891073,"uid":63113,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FxgzOp6.png\" data-thumbnail-sr